<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26> a ns1:CourseGuide ;
    ns1:hasCompetency <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CB10>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CB7>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CB9>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CE15>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CE17>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CE3>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CE8>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CG1>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CT10>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CT12>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CT7>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CT8> ;
    ns1:hasDidacticResource <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/didactic_resource/1>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/didactic_resource/2>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/didactic_resource/3>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/didactic_resource/4> ;
    ns1:hasEvaluation <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/evaluation> ;
    ns1:hasLearningResult <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/RA71>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/RA72>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/RA73> ;
    ns1:hasSyllabus <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/syllabus> ;
    ns1:inpersonHours "29 horas (37.2%)"@es ;
    ns1:numberOfCredits 3.0 ;
    ns1:otherInformation """Students will have access to all the resources and activities through the UPM's Moodle platform. Communication between students and teachers will preferably be done through the Moodle platform.
Nuclear Fusion is a new source of energy with enormous potential to be exploited. This potential can help us achieve several of the Sustainable Development Goals:
SDG7 Affordable and non-polluting energy: The potential for exploiting Nuclear Fusion is virtually inexhaustible. Therefore, sustainable use of this energy source can be made over time and it is also based on very abundant resources, so any nation can access this energy source. It is also an energy source with low greenhouse gas emissions and the generation of radioactive waste is much more limited than in nuclear fission technology.
SDG9 Industrial, innovation and infrastructure: The development of Nuclear Fusion still requires the development of new techniques and materials to be able to exploit it in a controlled and safe manner. These developments will generate a technological advance that the industry can take advantage of and therefore make the economies of the countries grow.
SDG13 Climate action: As Nuclear Fusion is a technology for energy production with low greenhouse gas emissions, it helps us mitigate climate change by reducing emissions from energy production."""@es ;
    ns1:periodEndingMonth "Junio"@es ;
    ns1:periodStartingMonth "Febrero"@es ;
    ns1:teachingPeriod "2025-26" ;
    ns1:teachingPeriodMonths "Febrero-Junio"@es ;
    ns1:totalHours "45 horas"@es ;
    schema:activitiesWorkload "100%"@es ;
    schema:courseSchedule <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/eventSchedule> ;
    schema:description "This course provides a comprehensive overview of nuclear fusion, covering everything from the fundamental plasma physics to the reactor engineering challenges and the profound societal impact of fusion energy. We'll explore magnetic confinement fusion (MFE), diving into the behavior of high-temperature plasmas with topics like kinetic and fluid descriptions, magnetohydrodynamics (MHD), plasma waves, and instabilities relevant to tokamaks and stellarators. We'll also examine the theoretical and experimental aspects of MFE, including plasma heating, current drive, and performance limits. Concurrently, we'll explore inertial confinement fusion (IFE), focusing on laser-plasma interactions, implosion dynamics, and target design. Finally, we'll delve into the engineering principles of future fusion power plants, addressing reactor concepts, blanket design, material challenges, superconducting magnets, and the safety and environmental considerations that will shape our energy future."@es ;
    schema:director <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/manuel.cotelo%40upm.es> ;
    schema:inLanguage "Inglés"@es ;
    schema:instructor <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/ea.vazquez%40upm.es>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/eduardo.oliva%40upm.es>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/manuel.cotelo%40upm.es>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/pedro.velarde%40upm.es> ;
    schema:name "Nuclear Fusion Technology"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CB10> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CB10" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Que los estudiantes posean las habilidades de aprendizaje que les permitan continuar estudiando de un modo que habrá de ser en gran medida autodirigido o autónomo./ Students have the learning skills that they require to pursue their studies in a largely self"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CB7> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CB7" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Que los estudiantes sepan aplicar los conocimientos adquiridos y su capacidad de resolución de problemas en entornos nuevos o poco conocidos dentro de contextos más amplios (o multidisciplinares) relacionados con su área de estudio/ Students are capable of applying their knowledge, understanding, and problem"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CB9> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CB9" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Que los estudiantes sepan comunicar sus conclusiones y los conocimientos y razones últimas que las sustentan a públicos especializados y no especializados de un modo claro y sin ambigüedades/ Students are capable of clearly and unambiguously communicating their conclusions, and the underlying knowledge and rationale to specialist and non"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CE15> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CE15" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Conocer los criterios básicos de seguridad y protección radiológica, el impacto de las radiaciones ionizantes y las tecnologías del blindaje contra las mismas./ Knowledge of the basic criteria of safety and radiological protection, the impact of ionizing radiation and shielding technologies against them."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CE17> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CE17" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Comprender los procesos que integran el ciclo de vida de los procesos energéticos, desde la obtención del recurso primario, hasta su desmantelamiento, y su integración en la economía circular./ Understand the processes that make up the life cycle of energy processes, from obtaining the primary resource, to its dismantling, and its integration into the circular economy."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CE3> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CE3" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Utilizar las herramientas necesarias para el diseño y análisis de sistemas de generación, trasformación, almacenamiento y utilización de energías nucleares, mecánicas, eléctricas, térmicas e hidráulicas./ Use the necessary tools for the design and analysis of systems for the generation, transformation, storage and use of nuclear, mechanical, electrical, thermal and hydraulic energies."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CE8> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CE8" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Disponer de habilidades, criterios y conocimientos para investigar, desarrollar e innovar en el campo de la energía: tecnologías renovables y no renovables, almacenamiento, vectores energéticos, en un contexto de decarbonización del sistema./ Skills, criteria and knowledge to research, develop and innovate in the field of energy: renewable and non"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CG1> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CG1" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Aplicar conocimientos de ciencias y tecnologías avanzadas a la práctica profesional o investigadora de la Ingeniería Energética./ Apply knowledge of advanced science and technology to the professional or research practice of Energy Engineering."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CT10> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CT10" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Conoce. Conocimiento de los temas contemporáneos./ Knowledge of contemporary issues."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CT12> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CT12" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Es bilingüe. Capacidad de trabajar en un entorno bilingüe (inglés/español). / Bilingual. Ability to work in a bilingual environment (English / Spanish)."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CT7> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CT7" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Comunica. Habilidad para comunicar eficazmente./ Communicate. Ability to communicate effectively."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/CT8> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CT8" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Entiende los impactos. Educación amplia necesaria para entender el impacto de las soluciones ingenieriles en un contexto social global./ Understand the impacts. Broad education to understand the impact of engineering solutions in a global social context."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/RA71> a ns1:LearningResult ;
    ns1:learningResultCode "RA71" ;
    ns1:learningResultDescription "Entender de los Principios de la Tecnología de Generación de Energía por Fusión Nuclear por Confinamiento Magnético e Inercial."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/RA72> a ns1:LearningResult ;
    ns1:learningResultCode "RA72" ;
    ns1:learningResultDescription "Conocer y analizar el estado actual de las instalaciones de Fusión Nuclear por confinamiento magnético e inercial."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/RA73> a ns1:LearningResult ;
    ns1:learningResultCode "RA73" ;
    ns1:learningResultDescription "Identificar las funciones y sistemas necesarios para el funcionamiento de una instalación de Fusión Nuclear y sus restricciones."@es .

