<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002038/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """Your final grade for this subject will be based on two components:

Exercises: 40% of your final grade. These must be submitted via the Moodle platform.
Exam: 60% of your final grade. This will include both multiple-choice questions and short problems.
Please note that you must achieve a minimum score of 4 out of 10 on each of these activities to pass the subject"""@es ;
